# Intel recommends reserving the following resources per PCIe TBT root port,
# from ADL BIOS Spec (doc #627270) Revision 0.6.0 Section 7.2.5.1.5
# - 42 buses
# - 194 MiB Non-prefetchable memory
# - 448 MiB Prefetchable memory
